# AGG.homes Static Landing Page

A minimal static real estate landing page built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Quick Start

1. Clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
3. Deploy to GitHub Pages (see Deployment section)

## Files

- `index.html` - Main landing page
- `css/styles.css` - Responsive styles
- `js/script.js` - Form validation
- `images/favicon.ico` - Favicon

## Deployment

1. Create GitHub repo: `agg-homes`
2. Push all files to `main` branch
3. Enable GitHub Pages: Settings > Pages > Deploy from `main` > `/`
4. Live at: `https://yourusername.github.io/agg-homes/`

## Setup

- Update `index.html` canonical URL and contact details
- Replace Unsplash image URLs with your own
- Configure form endpoint in `js/script.js` (Formspree)
- Submit sitemap to Google Search Console

## Features

✓ Responsive mobile-first design  
✓ SEO optimized (meta tags, sitemap, robots.txt)  
✓ Accessible (ARIA labels, WCAG AA contrast)  
✓ Form validation with error messages  

## Testing

```bash
npm install
npm test
npm run test:ui
```

See [TESTING.md](TESTING.md) for details.